    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At Level 20, you have realized that Biology is the future of Shinobi. </p><p>You can Select one Medical Ninjutsu of S- Rank or lower. </p><p>Once per Long rest you can cast the jutsu using CCD chakra with its cost rounded up to the nearest interval of 10. </p><p>If it restores hit points you must use Mending CCD Chakra. </p><p>if it deals damage, you must use Maiming CCD Chakra. </p><p>If it does both you must split the cost in between Maiming and Mending CCD chakra evenly.</p>",
